about the hit squad.

74
00:04:58.065 --> 00:04:59.534
- He was crazy about you. Bex.

75
00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:04.572
Losing you. that was all
that he cared about.

76
00:05:06.107 --> 00:05:11.378
Now. if he didn't tell you
the truth.

77
00:05:11.444 --> 00:05:13.114
